{"tid":273972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★全新設計40呎單位，3部iPhone都放不下！","createTime":"2017-06-07T03:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T06:26:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcdcb3f5f48f5082e0592c7b3492312ce4b569dc","tid":273972,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:32:47.000Z","msg":"香港納米樓愈起愈細，如果要住在相等於三分之一個車位大小的40呎迷你單位，闊度更只有50厘米，隨時連3部iPhone都放不下，你又願意嗎？<br />\n<br />\n「最細嘅單位可以係幾多呢？會唔會得返一幅牆？」設計師張智強(Gary)眼見香港納米樓愈起愈多，更愈起愈細，令他萌生設計意念。他用40呎空間，放滿生活必須的傢具，如床、電視和廚具等。部分傢具更一物多用，如書桌前的椅子便可變成坐廁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170607/bkn-20170607073000048-0607_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170607%2Fbkn-20170607073000048-0607_00822_001.html&d=s5EF9dUvn4yAA5qclk7%2B4U%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=53f18734\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170607/bkn-20170607073000048-0607_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b1b22523b1d59e71e00704dfe30f3936f3cd4829","tid":273972,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170607/photo/bkn-20170607073000048-0607_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170607104218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170607%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170607073000048-0607_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170607104218&h=40bd78d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"029eff52492837789e9b787e332bf7b0fa54993b","tid":273972,"uid":71833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:34:39.000Z","msg":"試下賣400萬"},{"pid":"f8d0612ec8a16e06174550c8400e47e1f687a2da","tid":273972,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下賣400萬</blockquote><br />\n600萬起"},{"pid":"1bb3be30f8c0e692ca5aa8020edea649027e624c","tid":273972,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r